{"word":"H7326 - רוּשׁ - rûwsh - roosh - Lack - குறைவு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>רוּשׁ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>rûwsh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>roosh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Lack / குறைவு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தாழ்ச்சியடை. எளியவன், தரித்திரன், திக்கற்றவன், ஏழை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be poor, to be in want, to lack"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be poor"},{"paragraph":"2) to be in want or hunger"},{"paragraph":"3) a poor man (substantive)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hithpolel) one impoverishing himself (participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>be destitute: - </i>lack, needy, (make self) poor (man)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7326 - רוּשׁ - rûwsh - roosh/7326\">H7326</a>, <a href=\"#/H7389 - רֵישׁ - rêysh - raysh/7389\">H7389</a>"}]}